nodes.text: The Eastport Docks was a location on the planet Coruscant. In 7956 C.R.C., a shipment containing several pallets of Moogan tea destined for the planet's underlevels was confiscated from the docks by the Coruscant Security Force based on a tip from Sundari Police Authority on the planet Mandalore.
Eastport Docks was first mentioned in the 2018 reference book Star Wars: Scum and Villainy: Case Files on the Galaxy's Most Notorious, which was written by Pablo Hidalgo.
